   <p>We are looking for a highly skilled and experienced financial controller to join our high-tech start-up company. The successful candidate will be responsible for overseeing the financial operations of the company, including monitoring the budget, mastering financial statements, technical accounting, and tax compliance. The financial controller will also be responsible for managing inventory cycle and pricing inventory and reporting to manager level on a monthly basis.</p>
   <p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>
