 <li>preparing financial statements and activity reports in accordance with IFRS;</li>
 <li>prepare reports that highlight business finances and forecasts to stakeholders;</li>
 <li>seek ways to improve financial allocations, or reduce expenses;</li>
 <li>audit or review financial statements, coordinating with external auditors as necessary;</li>
 <li>ensure regulatory compliance;</li>
 <li>supervise other employees who assist with reporting tasks within finance team as needed;</li>
</ul>
<p><span>Must-have qualifications:</span></p>
<ul>
 <li>Accounting background or experience with IFRS;</li>
 <li>At least 3 years of professional work experience or work experience as an auditor;</li>
 <li>Knowledge or familiarity with Mongolian taxation systems and regulations;</li>
 <li>Proficiency in English;</li>
 <li>Bachelor or higher degree in Accounting, Finance, Economics, or similar field;</li>
</ul>
<p><span>Nice-to-have qualifications:<span> </span></span>Either or more of the following:</p>
<ul>
 <li>ACCA or CFA pursuant or certified is a plus;</li>
 <li>Work experience within “Big Four” accounting firms is strongly preferred;</li>
 <li>CPTA certification is a plus;</li>
</ul>');
