INSERT INTO job_postings (id, job_page_url, position_name, organization_url, logo_url, organization_title, labor_function, posted_date_unix, description_html) VALUES (72, 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/heatseeker-2/jobs/52646305-customer-success-research-experimentation-specialist-australia#content', 'Customer Success: Research & Experimentation Specialist (Australia)', 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/heatseeker-2?filter=eyJqb2JfZnVuY3Rpb25zIjpbIkN1c3RvbWVyJTIwU2VydmljZSJdfQ%3D%3D#content', 'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/b64c5988-14f8-5cca-9633-8c78e36de069-1750177289', 'Heatseeker', 'Customer Service', 1749859200, '<div>
 <p>Are you a consultant, growth marketer or market researcher who thrives at the intersection of data, experimentation, and customer relationships? Do you want to move into a role where you can help enterprise teams run smarter tests and make better decisions, faster?</p>
 <p><strong>Heatseeker</strong> is the world’s first AI-powered market experiments platform, built for teams who want to replace guesswork with evidence.</p>
 <p>We help large companies validate messaging, value propositions, and go-to-market strategies through rapid, quant-based experiments—no more relying on dated research or gut feel. We’re hiring our <strong>first Customer Success Manager (CSM) </strong>in Australia.</p>
 <p>This role blends high-level strategy with hands-on execution. You’ll partner with some of the world’s most ambitious brands to help them use Heatseeker to uncover what really works—and what doesn’t.</p>
 <p>What You’ll Do:</p>
 <ul>
  <li><strong>Onboard and guide customers</strong> – Support enterprise clients from day one through scaling their experimentation efforts.</li>
  <li><strong>Coach teams on experiment design</strong> – Help customers run smarter tests and interpret the results with confidence.</li>
  <li><strong>Deliver real impact</strong> – Turn test outcomes into clear recommendations for GTM, messaging, or product direction.</li>
  <li><strong>Collaborate cross-functionally</strong> – Share feedback with product, help refine sales motions, and contribute to our overall growth strategy.</li>
 </ul>
 <p>What You Bring:</p>
 <ul>
  <li>A background in management consulting or research and experimentation - you bring structure, strategic thinking, and know how to drive results.</li>
  <li>Confidence working with data and growth strategies.</li>
  <li>Experience working with or supporting enterprise clients.</li>
  <li>An ability to translate technical detail into business impact.</li>
  <li>Sydney based - ability to be in office in a hybrid capacity.</li>
 </ul>
 <p>This is a unique opportunity to build out customer success for a fast-growing Martech AI company. If you’re energized by helping customers succeed—and love working in an early-stage, fast-moving environment—we want to meet you.</p>
</div>');
