</ul>
<p><strong>Training Delivery (20%)</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Deliver select training sessions (live or virtual), especially during onboarding or rollout of major new tools, features, or policies.</li>
 <li>Support group coaching sessions or small workshops in collaboration with trainers, QA, and workforce teams to reinforce content and drive behavioral change.<br><br></li>
</ul>
