 <li>Has a proven track record of success in analytics for performance marketing</li>
 <li>Has 4+ years of experience in marketing analytics</li>
 <li>Demonstrated experience in LTV estimation, attribution modeling, marketing mix modeling and marketing performance analysis</li>
 <li>Is highly skilled in SQL, R (Tidyverse) or Python</li>
 <li>Has 2+ years of experience using BI Tools (Tableau, Looker, etc.)</li>
 <li>Has strong storytelling skills with a track record of presenting to both technical and non-technical audiences</li>
 <li>Has strong problem-solving skills, with an ability to come to rigorous and defensible solutions to complex and open-ended problems</li>
