 <h3><strong>Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates &amp; Applicants</strong></h3>
 <p>If you’re applying from specific regions, your personal data may be processed in line with applicable privacy laws, including the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong> and the <strong>California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</strong>.</p>
