  <li>
   <p><span><span>Design eye-catching graphics for social media, blog, email, and digital campaigns</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Create short-form videos and motion graphics using Adobe After Effects (Reels, TikToks, product explainers, etc.)</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Assist in storyboarding and editing marketing videos</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Collaborate with the content and growth teams to bring creative campaigns to life</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Help maintain and evolve brand visual guidelines</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Support other marketing design needs as they arise</span></span></p></li>
 </ul>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Qualifications:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
 <ul>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Current student or recent grad in Graphic Design, Marketing, Communications, or a related field</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Strong portfolio showcasing design and video work</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Proficiency in Adobe Creative Suite—especially Illustrator, Photoshop, Premiere Pro, and After Effects</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Experience creating short videos for digital platforms (Instagram, YouTube, TikTok)</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>A keen eye for design, layout, typography, and color</span></span></p></li>
  <li>
   <p><span><span>Self-starter with a collaborative spirit and a desire to learn</span></span></p></li>
 </ul>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Why TomoCredit?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Join a team where your work makes a significant impact on the future of credit and banking. At TomoCredit, you’ll collaborate with seasoned FinTech executives from Square, Lending Club, and American Express. We’re committed to fostering a culture where people love what they do and the team they work with. Here’s what we offer:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
 <ul>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Competitive Salary</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span>: Reflecting your skills and experience.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
