  <li>Identify and execute strategic improvements in scalability, accuracy, and performance of forecasting systems</li>
  <li>Enhance developer experience, advocating best practices, and upgrading tooling within the data science and engineering teams</li>
  <li>Actually get things done, deciding yourself what to focus on — without bureaucracy</li>
 </ul>
 <p>✅<strong> Must-Have Skills</strong></p>
