  <li>Is <strong>comfortable around dogs of all sizes, breeds, and personalities</strong><br></li>
  <li>Can multitask with grace and keep calm under pressure<br></li>
  <li>Enjoys rolling up their sleeves and being present with the team on the floor<br></li>
  <li>Thrives in a role where no two shifts look the same</li>
 </ul>
 <h3><strong>🎁 Perks &amp; Benefits</strong></h3>
 <ul>
  <li>Competitive hourly pay starting at $18 an hour<br></li>
  <li>Discounts on Skiptown services<br></li>
