         <li><strong>Goal Setting &amp; Performance:</strong> Define and animate OKRs at both the team and individual levels.</li>
         <li><strong>Team Development:</strong> Build, mentor, and support team growth, ensuring a productive, motivated, and high-performing environment.</li>
         <li><strong>Workload &amp; Performance Management:</strong> Manage team workload, provide guidance, and set up quality indicators to monitor and improve performance.</li>
