  <li>
   <p>You take pride in every detail of the guest experience—from the warm welcome at the front desk to the buzz of the bar on a sunny Saturday.</p></li>
  <li>
   <p>You’re driven by metrics and can rally your team to hit sales, membership, and service goals.</p></li>
  <li>
   <p>You’re at your best in lively, fast-moving environments and love solving problems on the fly.</p></li>
  <li>
   <p>You care deeply about quality, integrity, and creating a welcoming space for all guests (two- and four-legged!).</p></li>
 </ul>
 <p><strong>As a Social Manager at Skiptown, you will:</strong></p>
 <ul>
