   <p>Own the overall guest experience in our Dog Social Club, including the park, bar, and concierge (front desk) areas.</p></li>
  <li>
   <p>Lead and develop the Concierge Team to deliver seamless check-ins, upsells, and support.</p></li>
  <li>
