<p>Openly is seeking a visionary and results-oriented <strong>Senior Director of Claims Product Management</strong> to lead the strategic direction and execution of our claims product portfolio. This new role will be instrumental in shaping the future of our claims experience, driving innovation, and ensuring operational excellence. Reporting to VP, Product &amp; Strategy, the Senior Director will partner closely with senior leadership across Product, Engineering, Claims Operations, and other key stakeholders to define and deliver world-class claims solutions that align with Openly\'s overall business strategy and enhance customer satisfaction.</p>
<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
