   <li>100% Employer Paid Top Health Care</li>
   <li>Bonus Eligible</li>
   <li>Unlimited Paid Time Off</li>
   <li>Stock in Vita Inclinata Technologies</li>
   <li>Employer Match 401k Program (6%)</li>
   <li>Additional benefits including dental, vision, and life insurance</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Vita Inclinata Technologies is an equal opportunity employer that values workplace diversity. We strive to create an inclusive workplace that embraces diverse backgrounds, life experiences, and perspectives. We do not discriminate on the basis of race, color, religion, sex (including pregnancy, sexual orientation, or gender identity), ancestry, national origin, veteran status, marital or family status, age (40 or older), disability and genetic information (including family medical history or any other characteristic protected by law). We do not tolerate unlawful discrimination in any employment decisions including recruiting, hiring, compensation, promotion, benefits, discipline, termination, job assignments or training.</strong></p>
