INSERT INTO `parser-db`.job_postings (id, job_page_url, position_name, organization_url, logo_url, organization_title, labor_function, posted_date_unix, description_html) VALUES (542, 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/testlio/jobs/51940134-freelance-software-tester-localization-testing-arabic#content', 'Freelance Software Tester (Localization Testing, Arabic)', 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/testlio?filter=eyJqb2JfZnVuY3Rpb25zIjpbIlF1YWxpdHklMjBBc3N1cmFuY2UiXX0%3D#content', 'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/17d9185b-1399-5bb7-b219-cf74aa4f6902-1748914598', 'Testlio', 'Quality Assurance', 1748908800, '<div>
 <p>Hi there! We are Testlio, a software testing company with its own freelance network. Our freelancers test apps from companies across the globe. Testlio is a great place for people who value the freedom and flexibility of remote work.<br><br>
  At the moment, we are looking for freelance software testers who speak <strong>Native/Bilingual </strong>Arabic to join us in testing a globally known social media app.</p>
 <p>We aim to ensure that our client’s app works properly. You will be asked to verify professional translations, ensuring that the app is culturally sensitive in your language.</p>
 <p>To participate in this project you will need to create an account on our platform. Through this account, we can assign you testing tasks. You will be asked to use our website for defect tracking and will be given some material to go through to prepare you for testing.</p>
 <h3 id="requirements">Requirements</h3>
 <ul>
  <li>You have to be at least <strong>18 years old</strong></li>
  <li>Location: <strong>Saudi Arabia</strong></li>
  <li>Availability: <strong>Weekly</strong> testing &amp; <strong>AdHoc </strong>testing</li>
  <li>Language:<strong> English (intermediate or higher)</strong> to read the instructions and communicate with the testing team, <strong>Native/Bilingual Arabic </strong>to verify the Arabic translation of the social media app</li>
  <li>Devices you may need:<strong> iOS mobile (iOS 18+) </strong>and<strong> Android Mobile (OS 13+) </strong></li>
  <li>Experience: Software testing experience is a plus. As part of the recruitment process, you will be asked to take a hands-on software testing exercise in which you will test a mock app. The mock app has some bugs planted in it; your task will be to find the bugs and report them. You will also be asked to take a Localization testing course and a short quiz to ensure you are well-prepared for the actual testing.</li>
 </ul>
 <h3 id="what-does-testing-look-like">What does testing look like?</h3>
 <ul>
  <li>Type of testing:<strong> Localization, Functional</strong></li>
  <li>Type of work:<strong> short-term, freelance</strong></li>
  <li>Workload:<strong> We expect a weekly workload of 5h for this project. However, as part of the Testlio network, you will also be eligible for other projects on our website. </strong></li>
  <li>The payrate for this is <strong>$18 USD / h</strong>
   <ul>
    <li>Payments are made every week via <strong>PayPal</strong> or <strong>Payoneer</strong>.</li>
   </ul></li>
 </ul>
 <h3 id="how-to-start">How to start?</h3>
 <ul>
  <li>Click on the Apply button, you will be taken through our account creation process
   <ul>
    <li>All freelance software testers must have an account on our platform. The testing task and run documentation will be hosted on our website, which you can only access if you have an account.</li>
   </ul></li>
  <li>You will need to ensure your profile is complete</li>
  <li>You will receive instructions on where to apply on our platform in an email</li>
  <li>You will be asked to go through some materials to determine your eligibility, we will share more details about these steps after you have finished creating an account.
   <ul>
    <li>If you have any questions or need help, please reach out to <a href="#">[email protected]</a> using the code <strong>SMARABIC </strong>in the Subject line/email body so we can quickly identify your request.</li>
   </ul></li>
 </ul>
 <h3 id="benefits-of-being-a-freelancer-at-testlio">Benefits of being a freelancer at Testlio</h3>
 <ul>
  <li>Flexible hours. You can create your schedule.</li>
  <li>100% remote. Always.</li>
  <li>Testing global-scale mobile apps to boost your skills and career.</li>
  <li>Getting paid by the hour, not by the bug.</li>
 </ul>
 <p>Looking forward to meeting you 🦁</p>
 <div>
  <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://platform.testlio.com/tester-signup?campaign=bd837454ac95a11a91800aac247255f9" role="link">Apply now</a>
 </div>
</div>');
