 <p>To participate in this project, you will need to create an account on our platform. Through this account, we can assign you testing tasks. You will be asked to use our website for defect tracking. You will be given some materials on our website that will help you understand the principles of software testing and how we operate in order to ensure you’re fully prepared for the tasks ahead.</p>
