 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Job Summary:</span></span></span></span></span></span><br><span><span><span><span><span><span>We are seeking a highly motivated and detail-oriented Business Analyst, Strategic Finance, to join our growing team. This role is critical to managing TomoCredit’s financial performance and driving strategic initiatives. As part of the Strategic Finance team, you will play a key role in ensuring our financial targets are met, exceeded, and optimized for long-term success.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
