  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Optimization:</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Proactively identify opportunities to exceed financial expectations where targets are on pace, driving continuous improvement in financial outcomes.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
