  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Strategic Support:</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Collaborate cross-functionally to support key strategic initiatives, providing financial expertise to ensure success.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Attention to Detail:</span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Maintain extreme precision and accuracy in all financial analyses, ensuring high-quality deliverables.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
 </ul>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Qualifications:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
 <ul>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Bachelor’s degree in Finance, Business, Economics, or a related field.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>2-4 years of experience in Investment Banking, Venture Capital (VC) / Private Equity (PE), or Corporate Finance at a top-tier technology company.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Exceptional analytical skills with a demonstrated ability to interpret complex financial data.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Extreme attention to detail and a high regard for precision in all aspects of work.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Strong proficiency in financial modeling and data analysis tools (e.g., Excel, SQL).</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to convey financial insights to non-financial stakeholders.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
  <li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Highly adaptable and thrives in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
 </ul>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Why TomoCredit?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
 <p><span><span><span><span><span><span>Join a team where your work makes a significant impact on the future of credit and banking. At TomoCredit, you’ll collaborate with seasoned FinTech executives from Square, Lending Club, and American Express. We’re committed to fostering a culture where people love what they do and the team they work with. Here’s what we offer:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
