  <li><span>Prioritize features and initiatives based on business value, customer needs, and technical feasibility.</span></li>
  <li><span>Work closely with UX/UI, R&amp;D, QA and support teams to ensure successful and timely delivery.</span></li>
  <li><span>Monitor product performance and analyze usage data.</span></li>
