  <li><span>3+ years of experience as a Product Manager in B2B SaaS</span><strong> - Must.</strong></li>
  <li><span>Excellent communication skills, with the ability to translate technical details into clear business value.</span></li>
  <li><span>Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities.</span></li>
  <li><span>Experience working with engineering, design and sales.</span></li>
  <li><span>Passion for creating intuitive products that users love.</span></li>
 </ul>
 <p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>
 <ul>
  <li><span>A fast-paced, innovative environment where your ideas truly matter and drive real impact!</span></li>
  <li><span>Major growth opportunities in a rapidly scaling global company.</span></li>
  <li><span>A vibrant, passionate team that\'s a blast to work with.</span></li>
  <li><span>Experience working with engineering, design and sales.</span></li>
  <li><span>Passion for creating intuitive products that users love.</span></li>
 </ul>
</div>');
INSERT INTO `parser-db`.job_postings (id, job_page_url, position_name, organization_url, logo_url, organization_title, labor_function, posted_date_unix, description_html) VALUES (612, 'https://jobs.techstars.comhttps://wellfound.com/company/sigma360/jobs/3266135-data-product-owner-ingestion-intelligence?utm_source=Techstars+job+board&utm_medium=getro.com&gh_src=Techstars+job+board', 'Data Product Owner, Ingestion & Intelligence', 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/sigma360-2-ee2e9a0d-3889-434b-9091-a3a8466b9eaf?filter=eyJqb2JfZnVuY3Rpb25zIjpbIlByb2R1Y3QiXX0%3D#content', 'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/4e6fde53-b720-5ab1-8b82-f3793fe38138-1748914063', 'Sigma360', 'Product', 1746403200, null);
INSERT INTO `parser-db`.job_postings (id, job_page_url, position_name, organization_url, logo_url, organization_title, labor_function, posted_date_unix, description_html) VALUES (613, 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/tive-2/jobs/52830094-software-engineer#content', 'Software Engineer', 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/tive-2#content', 'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/10417693-28ea-55db-8bfd-539a6d3b4770-1749087611', 'Tive', 'Product', 1750204800, '<div>
 <p dir="ltr"><span>At </span><a dir="ltr" href="http://tive.com/"><span>Tive</span></a><span>, we imagine a fully-transparent world in which everything and everyone is connected. We innovate beyond what the world thought possible—so what people hold near and dear arrives on time and in full.</span></p>
 <p dir="ltr"><span>We believe (and live!) four core values:</span></p>
 <ul>
  <li dir="ltr"><b><strong>Transparency First: </strong></b><span>We make everything visible so that everyone can operate better</span></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><b><strong>Always strive to make things simpler</strong></b></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><b><strong>We are One Team, we have each other\'s backs</strong></b></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><b><strong>Relentless iteration to optimize and improve</strong></b></li>
 </ul>
 <p dir="ltr"><span>Whether shipped by road, rail, ocean, or air, Tive reduces shipment delays, minimizes rejected loads, and decreases theft, damage, and spoilage. Our customers count on Tive to ensure that their shipments are delivered on time and in full—because every shipment matters.</span></p>
 <p dir="ltr"><span>As a </span><b><strong>Software Engineer</strong></b><span> at Tive, you will contribute to designing and developing a large-scale data processing and analytics system that helps our customers monitor, analyze, and predict shipments in the supply chain. You’ll work closely with a team of full-stack engineers, collaborating on technical solutions, writing high-quality code, and participating in code reviews and architecture discussions.</span></p>
 <p dir="ltr"><span>We highly value engineers who take initiative, demonstrate ownership over their work, and contribute to a culture of continuous improvement. We’re looking for someone who is eager to collaborate, share knowledge with teammates, and actively participate in technical discussions and decision-making. </span></p>
 <p dir="ltr"><b><strong>Our ideal candidate has:</strong></b></p>
 <ul>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>3+ years of successful history in software engineering positions,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Experience with multi-tier web application development,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Experience with AWS hosting environments,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Proficiency with server-side languages such as C#,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Proficiency with front-end frameworks such as Angular,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Familiarity with databases such as SQL Server and/or Postgres,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>A strong desire to learn, teach, and collaborate with the team.</em></i></li>
 </ul>
 <p dir="ltr"><b><strong>In addition, they may have:</strong></b></p>
 <ul>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Experience using Docker and/or Kubernetes to build containerized applications,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Deep understanding of SQL Server, including database design, T-SQL, stored procedures, indexing, and query optimization techniques.</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>Experience with big data streaming platforms such as AWS Kinesis or Apache Kafka,</em></i></li>
 </ul>
 <p dir="ltr"><b><strong>What you’ll be doing:</strong></b></p>
 <ul>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>You will contribute to all aspects of the software development lifecycle, from coding and testing responsive web applications to managing databases and APIs.</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>You will offer guidance to team members through code reviews, pair programming, and mentorship.</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>You will coordinate efforts as your team creates a data processing and analytics system,</em></i></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><i><em>You will work to build strong relationships with and support co-workers, including remote peers in other time zones.</em></i><br><br></li>
 </ul>
 <p dir="ltr"><b><strong>What does Tive offer?</strong></b></p>
 <ul>
  <li dir="ltr"><span>A chance to join what may very well turn out to be the most important company in your career.</span></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><span>The autonomy and resources to build what you know how to build.</span></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><span>Work with a committed global team that have each others back.</span></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><span>Office-based or hybrid options. Your choice. </span></li>
  <li dir="ltr"><span>Competitive equity to ensure all of our employees have a sense of ownership in the long-term success of Tive’s growth.</span><br><br></li>
 </ul>
 <p dir="ltr"><i><em>We celebrate diversity, and consider it key to our success as both a team and a company. We are proud to be an equal-opportunity employer, and we are committed to creating an inclusive environment of mutual respect for all employees.</em></i></p>
</div>');
INSERT INTO `parser-db`.job_postings (id, job_page_url, position_name, organization_url, logo_url, organization_title, labor_function, posted_date_unix, description_html) VALUES (614, 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/phoenix-tailings/jobs/52828373-6-6-business-development-leadership-development-program#content', '6.6. Business Development-Leadership Development Program', 'https://jobs.techstars.com/companies/phoenix-tailings#content', 'https://cdn.getro.com/companies/0064471a-ae9f-57e3-81bd-195a67672d6b-1747616937', 'Phoenix Tailings', 'Product', 1750204800, '<section>
 <div>
  <b>About Phoenix Tailings</b><span> </span>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>Phoenix Tailings is a rapidly growing clean mining and metals production startup dedicated to sustainable and economic critical metals production. Our mission is to be the world\'s first fully clean mining and metals production company, producing the resources needed for the next generation of our economy. </span>
 </div>
 <div>
  <b>Why Phoenix Tailings</b><span> </span>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>At Phoenix, we believe that nothing great is ever accomplished alone or without the passion of people who push and motivate one another. If you are someone who shares our relentless pursuit of a better future, passion for innovation, and are excited about working with some of the top innovators in the world, then this is the place for you. </span>
 </div>
 <div>
  <b>Our Values</b><span> </span>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>● </span><i>You are only crazy if you are wrong, it’s ok to be wrong</i>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>● </span><i>Lead with Compassion</i>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>● </span><i>Be Resourceful</i>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>● </span><i>Listen</i>
 </div>
 <div>
  <span>● </span><i>Hustle</i>
