  <span>We’re seeking a leader with deep expertise in modern Frontend frameworks like React, coupled with a strong design sensibility that bridges functionality and aesthetics. This individual should excel in mentoring team members, architecting complex systems, and collaborating across departments to translate business needs into seamless user interfaces. Above all, you should be passionate about using technology to make a meaningful social impact and thrive in a fast growth, mission-driven environment.</span>
